title: Stylish Studio- Must See! Hardwood/ Luxury Finishes/ WD in unit
posting_body: ['MODERN APARTMENTS', 'Custom-designed Plank Flooring', '9-Foot Floor to Ceiling Windows', 'Resident Controlled Nest Thermostats', 'Stainless Steel Bosch Appliances', 'Custom Closets with Built in Organizers', 'Quartz Countertops', 'Full Sized GE Washer-Dryer', 'LUXURY AMENITIES', 'Sun Deck w/ Grilling Stations, Hot Tub,  and Fire Pits', 'Outdoor Pool w/ Private Cabanas', 'Pool House w/ Ping Pong Table, Shuffleboard and more..', 'Demo Kitchen', 'Community Supported Agriculture Program', 'Dog Run', '24 Hour Concierge and Maintenance', 'Call or Email to schedule a tour.', 'We are available 7 days a week.', 'Downtown Apartment Company LLC', '730 N Wells Chicago, IL 60604', '312-772-3929', 'REF #134', 'Pictures are representative samples of the advertised unit.', 'In some cases, the actual units you tour may vary from the pictures based on the specific floor plan available.', 'Availability and prices are subject to change (and often do change daily).', 'Addresses, cross-streets or other geographic information, if provided, is intended to provide a general location of the advertised unit only; you should not rely on any address provided in this advertisement as an exact location of the unit.', 'Please contact us for exact addresses.', 'Units are leased unfurnished unless otherwise specified.', '12-month minimum lease term is standard for most units, but minimum term varies.', 'Equal housing opportunity.']
